<bibRefCitation author="Antoine, Ph. &amp; Camiade, D." box="[460,777,871,898]" pageId="30" pageNumber="181" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref22959" refString="Antoine, Ph. &amp; Camiade, D. (1995) Revision du genre Platygenia MacLeay et description d'une espece nouvelle (Coleoptera, Cetoniidae). Coleopteres, 1 (1), 1 - 8." type="journal article" year="1995">Antoine &amp; Camiade (1995)</bibRefCitation>
, who recognized four valid species. There is one species recorded for 
<collectingCountry box="[296,461,907,933]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="30" pageNumber="181">Guinea-Bissau</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Brivio, P. C." box="[475,616,907,934]" pageId="30" pageNumber="181" pagination="112 - 119" refId="ref24210" refString="Brivio, P. C. (1958) Contributo alla conoscenza della fauna coleopterologica della Guinea Portoghese. II - Cerambycidae, Chrysomelidae, Scarabaeidae. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali e del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Milano, 97, 112 - 119." type="journal article" year="1958">Brivio 1958</bibRefCitation>
